{"ha30db5c1g241fg4c26g80cfgbf629a835ac8": ["Walk well, friend.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "8b1e4b1d-5ec5-73ca-a300-6e816823b68b"], "hd47e3981g1833g4149gae46gb9cde5acaf65": ["Hm. You're not one of them.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "20fd1630-cb76-4f99-2133-192d74769a3f"], "h202a4511g2df4g4e96gba47ga2224562437d": ["You're one of them! Monster!", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "5b3afba3-0ccd-4c22-7e38-12fe990c3e84"], "h2eae864cgba18g4614gb94ag170e63224c5d": ["Monsters... everywhere... kill...", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "b73c9b33-16dc-b724-72d9-08ee770a8134"], "h6aa3e25cg5834g4626gbca6g030f0d1547f1": ["Look at me - I'm not a monster.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "c312119f-4737-c6ae-9dab-00169c3eaddd"], "ha4f476aeg8f28g4a9ag8faegf5df59fded9f": ["No... you're not. They were small like you, but uglier.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "eb289246-d7c2-8f30-710b-0b15445aa5ea"], "h056b6f5bg51f2g45cdg8bf2g85c330c5b2ad": ["I was ready to run you through. My mistake, friend.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "ff3bc3f3-7fc3-383e-22ca-1cda8d209014"], "h79ec497bg458fg429ag86a6gbe7773a5cc18": ["It's all right. What happened here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "f9738712-bee0-6307-73e8-9ad752fa6b42"], "hf633e221g2799g4548g9a35geb68dd9d4b2d": ["An attack. Monsters... little ones, and taller ones.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "74d395a2-2d23-1d4d-416f-2dfdfa63dd05"], "h37cac454g82f6g4efag9857g3055a1679983": ["They took the shiny one. He killed many.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "136b201d-a39d-6715-b92a-17b16edf7617"], "h28b3ee8dg0703g4b06gbed2gad4456d82753": ["Did you kill the goblin in the stable?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "607f54ac-acf2-34f4-a8e1-6d11d3419a52"], "h627d52d6g22e2g40bbg80a4g31cd35ec7036": ["Yes. It was screaming, waving around its metal.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "a8b06eb2-b5a6-c2c5-84fd-265b17fab281"], "hd5e06850g8cafg45e0gac71gab4e698f2cdb": ["I made him stop screaming.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "ddfec2a2-7c89-3d12-d7db-3a088fd83d2e"], "h6b73ad22ge70ag45e4g9bbeg285d4bb391b8": ["Do you know the dead ox outside?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "187ff0f0-81b9-7d90-9e12-7134924f4d4b"], "h94612714gb8a9g4f6dg9733gdb51bd1d3bd9": ["Him? He was the biggest. Now I'm the biggest.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "c140b7ad-2ccd-091e-73c7-05e643b5fb2c"], "h08e4efe7g79c5g4ea7ga9bdg3c834c4a4401": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "9dc8034e-8f66-5c98-f0fb-0bb0176142b5"], "h2f621f63ga5e0g4905g93ffg126bcee8c802": ["No. You're not one of them at all.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "b7cbb633-c71a-2eb8-a40c-78ebc046cfbe"], "h2d5411dag52dfg4981ga60dg6f4705abbfb1": ["LIAR! DIE!", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "ea22a6fb-f2b9-3d1a-8ddb-bc8e3df54a38"], "h72f64afcg5c85g44cag8df2g5d528ce0b380": ["Stay back. I don't want to hurt you, but I will.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "04980098-517c-bac3-1049-b8df9879611c"], "h3acd306bga78dg4c1bga773g20611c98dc35": ["You'd give me a choice? Hm. You're not like them.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "c8fe40e0-a4bb-5a9e-c21c-aed42b8eaaaa"], "h761d53dcgf6bfg418cg9474g70d0797da928": ["NO! DIE!", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "593bfdfb-b3d2-41a9-aa42-95f53a193192"], "hea6b3430gf95fg4693gbc04g87fdabada98a": ["Calm, friend. I won't harm you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "34c78a98-ca08-75e1-32ab-2605cf9f3209"], "he66033b1g0039g4d0cgb636gba51fe99631b": ["You speak to me? The monsters only scream.", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "a6c6b42e-3901-b8fe-c7a9-4005ec839653"], "hf580eb93g93f6g45beg8b40g490070b78074": ["Back down, beast, or I'll snap off your horns.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "9363a4c1-e463-3b45-6165-381a616e99de"], "h37700d2bg48a0g47e6g8a30g847e795c6beb": ["<i>Defend yourself.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "f69ca4b0-4247-e433-17db-493ff550743c"], "hb7b55059gc664g4ddcg886dg06cd46b20b22": ["*The creature turns a piece of cud around its mouth, chewing contentedly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "53e5fda1-fcf3-091e-a211-71225a1a1c8b"], "h559121d0g743eg4c8bg96cfgceb4b2baafb9": ["*Sniff.*", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "7841e242-0e4c-40bf-9df8-fb270b3ded45"], "h66b8564bg0cf0g4425g8781ge3ec3e867d96": ["*Grunt!*", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "bd7061b8-500d-78d9-641a-8620c45a4126"], "h442fbe44gab45g447bgae94g6c7c11d8796d": ["*The ox tenses, horns lowered in your direction.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "e5060e2b-1024-80cf-42ba-7f988d1a9256"], "h8576f786g6d63g4685gbfb2g9c6127eb2cde": ["<i>Back away.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "0328e776-67c9-78a3-4f0e-f36fecc1695b"], "h4286c135gb895g48f6g9b8ag91835d71d450": ["*Bellow!*", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "9e082e23-df7a-4825-4dab-bb48b3158440"], "h83d1f350ge515g4c1dgb5bcgde3ba4f591e1": ["<i>Interpret his behaviour.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "4185961d-40ec-6d21-5710-9902ef782fa5"], "he9d09c78g43beg40c3gac7eg8d04c8292c6c": ["*His hide twitches, every muscle primed to bolt. He's <i>terrified</i>.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "c95e9ce4-945a-65b0-7bfc-b16b09f2fd82"], "h53240a1fga539g4f19gb6e4g66bb13b88bb5": ["<i>Hold out your hands peacefully.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "8e3a7a10-4504-f9eb-c1ce-5bec5d8e8c60"], "h52726958ge67bg4ed7ga8abgdd7804c9c538": ["*The ox calms, his tail swishing a satisfied arc.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "aa392c2c-f931-bfec-b635-7c78d984d5aa"], "h232c6946ge21fg44c7g928cg553f12638d57": ["*Moo.*", "c69aa4c1-bac2-401f-b4ec-cce8d545ba7c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "48c7f833-6102-d147-f014-2d76f6f129a8"], "h860b81c7g5b4dg4fedg9226g10ff0d0abc92": ["*You manage only to agitate him more.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "c2efd93f-5090-e7f0-ec94-6315be7e4bb6"], "hb39f4f44gf1d0g4f4dg98eag38db2c13a176": ["*His glassy eyes roll, wild with fear, as he begins to charge.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "8158eac1-01a1-14be-06ec-15c191e2717d"], "hfb9eef1bg52d1g4488g9936gc93e4f684522": ["<i>Square your stance and face him directly.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "d213a35b-68e5-8de6-6f34-fbb7908c7667"], "h45785600gf801g488eg8617g07048a377cd4": ["*He huffs and, after a moment, appears to relax.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "99675150-f9c7-b15b-a5c6-38e654f0a785"], "h47039087g15e6g4963gb1fbgf973619ea50a": ["<i>Roar at the beast.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "b91335ee-86af-799f-56ae-3c6466dd48bc"], "ha3bc6ddeg2e78g4f5cg8577g911c22b15a5f": ["<i>Bow deeply - a submissive gesture.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "065343d4-f402-9dbc-ffac-6757ff9a8dcf"], "h3765fab3g241fg4914g8b1eg5e021f284e24": ["<i>Attack first.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "1b6ab9b4-8411-94eb-01bf-150d50932705"], "h146ba09eg7474g4ab4gac16gfd5e835fd8bd": ["*You gather nothing from his intense stare.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "74d7fe7a-6262-76a1-2eb6-26daa1b065ef"], "h7b4ccffag5524g488fga6ccg2fb9d7d4b315": ["<i>Defend yourself.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_OxAlive.html", "61408171-7ec5-981b-594b-429c00753929"]}